<h2 class="page-title text-center">Role/Skills framework System</h2>

<div class="row gutter-top">
    <p class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-center">Over time we will accumulate experience in the roles we have. We learn as a second nature to see patterns and do things that just work. These patterns and best practices are something that we as workers need experience and guidance to discover.</p>
    <p class="col-md-3 col-md-offset-8"><i>Chrisitan Dalager, Eksponent </i></p>
